          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can I use the same image across all social media platforms?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "While 1200x630 pixels (1.91:1) works as a shared link preview across most platforms, each platform has unique requirements for profiles, stories, and feed posts. A 1080x1080 square image works on most feeds, but you'll get better results by optimizing dimensions per platform."
